title: One Kombucha
description: Kombucha bar with various rotating flavors of Kombucha on tap such as lemon ginger, Apple spice,  blueberry, peach ginger, and hibiscus rose. Kombucha is available for drinking at the bar or to go in growlers. Small menu of items including miso soup, three types of salads (two organic), olive platter, and organic guacamole salsa and chips. Also offers local organic produce for sale from Kai Kai Farm, Chunky Dunkies local raw cookies and brownies, and other raw crackers and snacks in a cold case. The store also sells miscellaneous items like Kombucha soap.
